snippet.title: Sumikko Water Detailed Gameplay Walkthrough
snippet.description: In this video I do a detailed walk-through of the Sumikko Water, including how to navigate the device. I also have a full English translation guide uploaded on my website which you can check out here (scroll to the bottom where it says Sumikko Water): https://fuzzy-n-chic.com/pages/tamagotchi-guides-charts-translations-more
